data.name: AlreadyTransformedFinalBlock
data.value: This transform has already transformed its final block and can no longer transform additional data.

data.name: DuplicateCryptoConfigAlias
data.value: Alias '{0}' already exists in the CryptoConfig2 map.

data.name: EmptyCryptoConfigAlias
data.value: Null or empty CryptoConfig aliases are invalid.

data.name: InvalidChainingModeName
data.value: CNG chaining modes cannot have empty names.

data.name: InvalidIVSize
data.value: The specified IV was not long enough. IVs must be the same length as the block size.

data.name: InvalidPadding
data.value: The padding on the block is invalid and cannot be removed.

data.name: InvalidRsaParameters
data.value: The specified RSA parameters are not valid; both Exponent and Modulus are required fields.

data.name: InvalidSignatureHashAlgorithm
data.value: The hash algorithm is not supported for signatures. Only MD5, SHA1, SHA256,SHA384, and SHA512 are supported at this time.

data.name: InvalidTagSize
data.value: The specified tag is not a valid size for this implementation.

data.name: KeyMustBeRsa
data.value: The specified key must be an RSA key

data.name: MissingIV
data.value: No IV was given, and the specified CipherMode requires the use of an IV.

data.name: TagIsOnlyGeneratedAfterFinalBlock
data.value: Authentication tags are only available after the final block has been transformed.

data.name: TagIsOnlyGeneratedDuringEncryption
data.value: Authentication tags are only generated during encryption operations, and cannot be retrieved from a decryption transform.

data.name: UnsupportedCipherMode
data.value: The specified CipherMode is not supported with BCrypt symmetric algorithms.

data.name: UnsupportedPaddingMode
data.value: The specified PaddingMode is not supported
